<h2 class="line">Summary</h2>


<p>Noridian Healthcare Services, LLC, a Medicare contractor, understated its allocable postretirement benefit (PRB) costs for the Medicare segment by $540,000 and overstated its allocable PRB costs for the Other segment by $1.5 million for calendar years 2006 through 2010. </p>



